{"tid":1434848,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung 將當年諷刺 Apple 移除 3.5mm 耳機端口的廣告下架","createTime":"2019-08-09T01:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T08:55:47.000Z","uid":1121,"like":79,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"35e700775d996eea5b9504046f9aa9d2700f1c19","tid":1434848,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:40:10.000Z","msg":"Galaxy Note 10 推出後，其中一個改變就是將 3.5mm 耳機端口移除，改為一個 USB-C 接口。原本這改動相當合理，也是大勢所趨。不過有趣的就是 Samsung 竟將 2017 年的一個諷刺 Apple 移除 3.5mm 耳機端口的廣告悄悄下架，無法從 Samsung Youtube 頻道找到（但秘魯 Samsung Youtube 當有影片）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/ScreenShot190526013126-51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2FScreenShot190526013126-51.jpg&h=2ff87e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當年這個廣告在 2017 年播放，當年用作宣傳 Galaxy Note 8，而 2017 年的 iPhone 則為 iPhone X。廣告裡看到一對情侶，男的是用 iPhone 女的是用 Samsung 手機，當中取笑 iPhone 沒有 3.5mm 耳機，令主角一邊充電一邊插耳機時非常不便。時至今日，無線充電的流行以及無線耳機變得普及，用戶已經不再介意沒有 3.5mm 插孔了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yxuHJv1_big\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyxuHJv1_big&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCLCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=98e234d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yxuHJv1_big</a>"},{"pid":"0fefc9b6bdd2654f90c7982db7e7087eb8ebe520","tid":1434848,"uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b59588db077123d820ef1f743706bacf002e1d","tid":1434848,"uid":1552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a2ca6c8335240ce5d5bd5243ca2cca406dac77","tid":1434848,"uid":199501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:43: